title: Ifish Season 7 Episode 2 720p [Mystic]
description:
Ifish Season 7 Episode 2 Aired 9th September 2012



 	

This week we go on a wild ride as I try to fulfil a boyhood dream.  My plan is to catch a fish bigger than the boat I am in and the only thing that may bring me unstuck is that the fish is a lot bigger than I hoped for!!  Jervis Bay really turns it on for this one.
